OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1781866972
OL,3,CFifa changes anthem rules after Tuchel
OL,4,Ccomplaint over photographers
OL,6,FFifa has taken action after England
OL,7,Fhead coach Thomas Tuchel complained
OL,8,Fthat a swarm of photographers
OL,9,Fobstructing his view during the
OL,10,Fnational anthem had "ruined" his
OL,11,Fexperience.
OL,13,FThe German steered England to a 4-2
OL,14,Fwin over Croatia in their first World
OL,15,FCup match on Wednesday, but said he
OL,16,F"could not see" his team while God
OL,17,FSave The King was being sung ahead of
OL,18,Fkick-off.
OL,26,@rD@UOUrD@\O]
