PN,31502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1781866972
OL,3,CFifa changes anthem rules after Tuchel
OL,4,Ccomplaint over photographers
OL,6,FTuchel's complaint has clearly been
OL,7,Flistened to, because the Press
OL,8,FAssociation understands Fifa will now
OL,9,Fallow coaches to stand to the left or
OL,10,Fto the right of the photographers
OL,11,Fduring the national anthems, to ensure
OL,12,Fthey have a clear view of their
OL,13,Fplayers.
OL,15,FThe change took effect for the first
OL,16,Fgame on Thursday between the Czech
OL,17,FRepublic and South Africa, sources
OL,18,Fclose to the global governing body
OL,19,Fsaid.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
