OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1781866972
OL,3,CFifa changes anthem rules after Tuchel
OL,4,Ccomplaint over photographers
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FIt is understood photographers will
OL,12,Fnot be moved, but may be bunched
OL,13,Fslightly more closely together.
OL,15,FTuchel said after Wednesday's match:
OL,16,F"I have to tell you something, I am
OL,17,Fbegging Fifa to change the position of
OL,18,Fthe photographers in the national
OL,19,Fanthem because I could not see my team
OL,20,Fin the national anthem.
OL,26,@xD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
