OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1781866972
OL,3,CFifa changes anthem rules after Tuchel
OL,4,Ccomplaint over photographers
OL,6,F"I was waiting for this moment. It was
OL,7,Fa very, very special moment today and
OL,8,FI was standing in front of a wall of
OL,9,F50 photographers, half a metre away,
OL,10,Fand I could not see one single player.
OL,11,FIt ruined a little bit my experience.
OL,13,F"It is very emotional. When I was
OL,14,Fyoung and when I started coaching,
OL,15,Fthis was too big to dream of this kind
OL,16,Fof occasion."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUxD@MO]
