PN,31505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1781866972
OL,3,CFifa changes anthem rules after Tuchel
OL,4,Ccomplaint over photographers
OL,6,FThe AT&T Stadium in Dallas, where the
OL,7,Fmatch was played, is quite unique in
OL,8,Fthis regard because of the small
OL,9,Fdistance between the touchline and the
OL,10,Fdugouts, meaning photographers are
OL,11,Fextremely close to the coaches.
OL,13,FHowever, it is understood that giving
OL,14,Fcoaches the option to move left or
OL,15,Fright will apply at all venues.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/5
